Name: Star Flakes
Desc: Increases all team members' DEF by 35%, lasting for 30m. Only effective on your own Resonators in Co-op Mode.
Bg: A snack popular among the children of Jinzhou, made with deep-fried meat bits of starry shapes and served with a special power dip. It is said that you can make a wish after eating it. "One star, two stars... you can't make a wish without eating it!"
